TextEng: Can I just ask you a quick question?
Text: 잠깐만 빠르게 질문 하나만 해도 돼요?

TextEng: Very well. I'll wait.
Do you know anything about what's going on in Luskan?
Text: 러스칸에서 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있는지 아세요?

TextEng: What are all these people here for?
Text: 이 사람들 다 뭐 때문에 여기 온 거예요?

TextEng: Anything interesting about the patrons?
Nevermind.
Who owns this place?
What's so strange about Zamithra?
Oh. Do you feel the same as she does?
Me just gots quick question me ask.
Okay, me wait.
Me gots questions about Luskan. You know anything?
Text: 나 러스칸에 대해 질문 있어. 뭐 알아?

TextEng: Why these people is in here?
You see any people in here? Seem different?
Text: 여기 사람들 중에 누가 특이해 보여?

TextEng: Me ask who owner is.
Me not ask anything.
Why Zamithra strange to you? What you see?
Me wonders if you feel same way? Hates men?
Text: 나 궁금해. 너도 같은 생각이야? 남자 싫어해?

TextEng: A minotaur? Tell me about him.
What you mean minotaur? Tell.
What was so strange about Zamithra?
Why Zamithra strange to you? What you see?
